  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6297836">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6297836/" class="title-link">只是一本二校样的稿件（不对内容做评价）</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6297836"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/37933748/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/37933748/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">fukaiumi</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-24"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-24 13:56:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6297836_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不谈内容。这本书只是二校样的稿件。     首先，校对。版式错误随处可见对案例的评述，字体，格式不统一。      其次，编辑。这本书翻译很糟糕，很容易看出是用软件弄出来整理的。学者的翻译可能更烂，语言会很生涩、学术，但是这是他们的领域。但这本书是面对大众的，所以编辑...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6297836/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">15有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6297836_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6297836_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7186821">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7186821/" class="title-link">原书很不错，中文翻译：差！差！差！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7186821"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/34911653/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34911653-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/34911653/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我叫张富贵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-11-10"
      class="main-meta">2014-11-10 23:34:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7186821_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  Copi这本书非常适合逻辑学入门，知识要点与他的《introduction to logic》基本一样，就是精简版，但是书要薄很多，读起来很快。 但是胡泽洪&amp;赵艺等翻译的实在太烂了，非常不负责任。作为博导、硕导名字却挂在这样的译作上，自己也不觉得丢人么？就算是学生翻译你来捡现成的挂名...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7186821/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7186821_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7186821_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
